Step 1: Study Phishing Attacks

Learned about phishing, spear phishing, and smishing

Understood how attackers trick users using fake emails and websites

Step 2: Phishing Simulation (Safe)

Used sample phishing emails and URLs

No real phishing emails were sent

Simulation was done using datasets and online analysis tools

Step 3: Detection Techniques

Checked suspicious URLs

Analyzed email content and headers

Identified red flags (fake domains, urgency, spelling errors)
